Description: A Shiny application for integrative enrichment analysis and
    visualization of multiple gene datasets. richStudio enables users to perform
    functional enrichment analysis (GO, KEGG, Reactome), cluster functionally
    related terms using multiple algorithms (richR, hierarchical, DAVID), and
    visualize results through interactive plots including bar plots, dot plots,
    heatmaps, and network graphs. Supports session save/load for reproducible
    analyses.
